abstract: Israeli military reports Palestinian militants launched two rockets from Gaza; second attack in eight days is believed to be by smaller, more radical groups than Hamas, signalling internal Palestinian tensions.
lead_paragraph: Palestinian militants launched two rockets from Gaza toward southern Israel late Wednesday, the Israeli military said.

headline.main: Gaza: Militants Fire Rockets Into Israel
headline.print_headline: Middle East; Gaza: Militants Fire Rockets Into Israel
